# VaibCask Repository Configuration
# Format: name|url|branch|install_method
#
# Install methods:
#   c_and_pip    - make opt then pip install -e . --no-deps
#   pip_no_deps  - pip install -e . --no-deps (deps in Dockerfile)
#   pip_editable - pip install -e . (standalone package)
#   scripts_only - add to PYTHONPATH and PATH only
#   reference    - clone for reference, do not install
#
# Order matters: repos are cloned and installed in this order.
# Lines starting with # are comments.
